Ranger Help for: pecking birds
================================

SYNTAX:      rbird <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   6
BASE SP:     25
SKILL TYPE:  religious

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to call upon a flock of birds to peck and
harass a target. The birds swoop down and attack, dealing minor damage
and distracting the enemy. While the damage is not great, the
distraction can disrupt an opponent's concentration and give the
Ranger an advantage. The number and ferocity of the birds depend on
the Ranger's guild level and connection to Gaia.
